<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[هلن]</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>: (الهِلْيَوْنُ،<span class="c5"> كبِرْذَوْنٍ:</span> نَبْتٌ م) مَعْروفٌ <span class="c2">(حارٌّ رَطْبٌ باهِيٌّ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>(وهِلَيْنِيَةُ) ،<span class="c5"> مُصَغَّراً:</span> اسمُ <span class="c2">(امْرأَةٍ)</span> .<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
